This library allow you to use timer such in Automation. 
The library uses the millis() function.
The delay() function is not used.
Timer TON starts after a time your event is true.
Timer TOF starts immediately and stops after a time your event is false.
Square waves are several waves of signal to blink led's or else.
Install the library in you Arduino IDE.
Open the examples for the "examples" folder.
Thanks.
